397
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:39,080
<i>Rangrang, I can't leave the office yet.</i>

398
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:41,480
<i>I don't think I can make it
to the seminar.</i>

399
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,160
<i>It's okay.</i>

400
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:46,480
<i>It's just a talk about a new product.</i>

401
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:47,680
<i>There will be a recording.</i>

402
00:26:47,760 --> 00:26:49,280
<i>You can watch it later.</i>

403
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:50,880
<i>You don't necessarily have to be here.</i>

404
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,680
<i>But it's your first product.</i>

405
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,360
<i>It's not the last one.</i>

406
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,560
<i>Rangrang, you've got this!</i>

407
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:06,080
It's about time. Let's go in.

408
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,000
Come on.

409
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:07,920
Let's go.

410
