The wide range of applications
of industrial drones

411
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,720
makes them
unlike consumer and military drones,

412
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,840
which have clear usage scenarios

413
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:15,840
and functions.

414
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:17,880
So now, the conflict is the gap

415
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,560
between the users' higher demands

416
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:22,120
and the product's performance

417
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,680
and service.

418
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,640
Today,

419
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:32,680
Luming is not just launching a new drone,

420
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:35,000
but also an all-new system

421
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:36,880
that can be used in various fields.

422
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:39,160
The launch of the CW-003

423
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:41,240
will open up a whole new world of demand

424
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:42,840
in the market.

425
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:43,800
Thank you.

426
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:48,560
