LUMING TECHNOLOGY, DRONE SEMINAR

427
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:50,520
All technical questions about drones

428
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:51,960
have been asked already.

429
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:54,240
May I ask you a personal question?

430
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:55,960
Sure.

431
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:57,120
We all know

432
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,640
that there were many difficulties

433
00:27:58,720 --> 00:28:01,120
in the research process for this drone.

434
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:03,960
As the youngest
aircraft manufacturing engineer

435
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:05,560
at Luming,

436
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:08,560
what are the convictions
that sustained you

437
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,960
to complete this project?

438
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:24,160
I used to be

439
00:28:25,360 --> 00:28:27,000
a person with no self-confidence.

440
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:29,960
Even before high school,

441
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:31,920
I had low self-esteem.

442
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:34,200
I always thought

443
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:36,040
I would live out my life in mediocrity.

444
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,480
That was until I met someone.

445
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:41,560
Every time I look at her,

446
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:44,080
I see myself in her eyes.

447
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:46,400
I have always wondered

448
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,760
why someone like her,

449
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,960
who is as bright as the sun, exists.

450
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:55,400
When I failed,

451
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:57,840
when I ran into difficulties,

452
00:28:58,560 --> 00:28:59,880
when I wanted to give up,

453
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,400
she would tell me,

454
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,480
"It's okay.

455
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:08,040
To me, you are the best."

456
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:13,600
I don't think
anyone can resist such favoritism.

457
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,560
Not to mention me,

458
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:19,840
who has never received
such partiality before.

459
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,720
Because of her unreserved faith in me,

460
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,640
I believe

461
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:30,440
I should continue to persevere for her.

462
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,280
I have made her cry again.

463
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:44,760
I'll have to cheer her up when I get home.

464
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:07,440
<i>We should all</i>

465
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:09,000
<i>receive the same amount of love.</i>

466
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:12,000
<i>We should all receive so much love.</i>
